This repository is about file server using linaro-license-protection.
If you don't want to create docker image, then skip 1-5 steps.

1. ubuntu 16.04 base pull
$ docker pull ubuntu:16.04

2. user add
Create base docker image.
$ docker run --name myubuntu ubuntu:16.04
$ docker attach myubuntu
# adduser nexell
# exit
$ docker commit -a "nexell" -m "ubuntu 16.04 adduser nexell" myubuntu nexell/ubuntu16-04

3. Create base fileserver docker image
$ docker build -t nexell/fileserver-base .

4. Create release server docker image
$ cd deploy-releases
$ docker build -t nexell/fileserver-releases .

5. Create snapshot server docker image
$ cd deploy-snapshot
$ docker build -t nexell/fileserver-snapshot .

6. Run fileserver docker container
$ ./run.sh
